	(2, 1, '2014-08-02 03:57:02', '2014-08-02 03:57:02', 'This section you can find tabs and playing demo of each song.They\'re totally free, just click on the link of the song you want, and start learning right away.\r\n\r\nPlease note that I do not own the tabs, most of them are on the internet, I just collected them and list here, they\'re all quality tabs I think.\r\n\r\nIf you want to support me, you can make a donation through Paypal here:[paypal-donation]\r\n\r\nThank you and enjoy :)', 'Sheets & Tabs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2017-06-12 09:28:43', '2017-06-12 02:28:43', '', 0, 'http://stenfingerstyle.rakuyomi.net/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
